    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.01)))
    tmp = (0.22 + wp.cos(v2))
    v2 = wp.sin(v1)
    v0 = ((v0 * (v0 + 0.77 / v1 + 0.11)) / (0.35 * wp.sin(v1 + 0.04)))
